Step 1: Start
Step 2: Move Input Data and Output Address into Registers
Step 3: Clear Carry
Step 4: Move First Operand into Accumulator
Step 5: Add Second Operand Using Accumulator
Step 6: Store Result in Destination Register
Step 7: Increment Output Address Pointer
Step 8: If no carry, go to Step 11
Step 9: Store Carry in AL
Step 10: Move AL to Output Address
Step 11: Stop